1.0.2

New: In the receivables table, the column Order now contains an link to the corresponding order form.

New: A delivery services provider can now be specified when creating a new order.

New: Order creation, production, printing and collecting is now possible from icons-based order management window.

New: shift_closures.zul now shows canceled closures too. So, a new decision was added to check canceled shift closures 
	in table "metamodel"."ResponsibilityFilter"
	
New: A checker is authorized to record and cancel shift closures.

New: Only managers can cancel past shift closures.

New: When changing an order's customer, previous and new customer are now logged.

New: When changing an order's delivery provider, previous and new provider are now logged.

New: Cancellations shift closure report added (removed ordered items, removed order additions, and changes on order customer and delivery provider).

Fix: Auditor responsibility was able to record and cancel a shift closure. These rights were removed from table 
	"metamodel"."ResponsibilityFilter"
	
Fix: A bug in FUNCTION soberano."fn_Stock_restoreToStateBefore"(startdatetime timestamp with time zone, inventoryitem character varying) prevented
	restoring stock to its state before the recalculation starting date.
	
Fix: Logs of soberano."fn_Order_changeDeliveryProvider" and soberano."fn_Order_changeCustomer" were wrongly translated and shown in shift closure
	cancellations report.

User manual: 1) pag. 18, 21, 22, 25: asistente de administrador, cajero, contador y jefe de turno solo pueden cancelar cierre del turno actual.
			2) pag. 21: se autoriza al cajero a cerrar turno.
			3) pag. 102: “las existencia” por “las existencias”.
			4) pag. 134, 135, 136: se actualizan los formularios de adición de artículos mediante iconos, permitiéndose producir, facturar e imprimir pedido desde esos formularios, así como crear un nuevo pedido.
			5) referencias no resueltas apuntando al procedimientos de configuración global.